To find out how many photon blasts Captain Marvel has left after using some against the Skrulls and Kree, we first need to determine how many she used in total for both fights.

SECTION 2
Captain Marvel initially had 5000 photon blasts. She used 2000 against the Skrulls and 500 against the Kree. To find out how many are left, we can subtract the number she used from the total amount:

\begin{equation}
\text{{Number of Photon Blasts Left}} = \text{{Total Photon Blasts}} - \text{{Used Against Skrulls}} - \text{{Used Against Kree}}
\end{equation}

Plug in the values given in the problem:

\begin{equation}
\text{{Number of Photon Blasts Left}} = 5000 - 2000 - 500
\end{equation}

Calculate the result:

\begin{equation}
\text{{Number of Photon Blasts Left}} = 5000 - 2500 = 2500
\end{equation}

So, Captain Marvel has 2500 photon blasts left.

